t: "And Satan will say ňĻto his followersňļ after the judgment has been passed, ‚ÄúIndeed, God has made you a true promise.¬†I too made you a promise, but I failed you. I did not have any authority over you. I only called you, and you responded to me. So do not blame me; blame yourselves. I cannot save you, nor can you save me. Indeed, I denounce your previous association of me with God ňĻin loyaltyňļ. Surely the wrongdoers will suffer a painful punishment.‚ÄĚ"